<p>Jacob is currently employed as a postdoctoral research associate working on the <a href="https://research-information.bris.ac.uk/en/projects/rework-of-mobile-phone-app-development-for-drought-adaptation-in-">Mobile phone App Development for Drought Adaptation in Drylands-MADDAD</a> project. In this project, we are researching how to best deploy information technology to benefit Kenyan farmers and pastoralists at risk of drought. Outside of work, he enjoys playing guitar, camper vans, and keeping fit.</p>
